OL,3,CGordon Ramsay urges cyclists to wear
OL,4,Chelmets after 'really bad accident'
OL,6,FIn an Instagram video on Saturday, he
OL,7,Fshowed a purple bruise which appeared
OL,8,Fto cover a significant portion of his
OL,9,Fchest.
OL,11,FWhile his hands were shaking, Ramsay
OL,12,Fsaid: "Hey guys, it's Gordon. I'd like
OL,13,Fto share a very important message with
OL,14,Fyou all.
OL,16,F"You know how much I love cycling and
OL,17,Ftriathlons and Ironman (races) etc and
OL,18,Fthis week, unfortunately, I had a
OL,19,Freally bad accident and it really
OL,20,Fshook me and honestly I'm lucky to be
OL,21,Fhere.
