OL,3,CGordon Ramsay urges cyclists to wear
OL,4,Chelmets after 'really bad accident'
OL,6,F"Those incredible trauma surgeons,
OL,7,Fdoctors, nurses in the hospitals
OL,8,Flooked after me this week, they were
OL,9,Famazing, but honestly you've got to
OL,10,Fwear helmets.
OL,12,F"I don't care how short the journey
OL,13,Fis. I don't care... these helmets cost
OL,14,Fmoney, but they're crucial, even with
OL,15,Fa kid's short journey, they've got to
OL,16,Fwear a helmet now.
OL,18,F"I'm lucky to be standing here. I'm in
OL,19,Fpain. It's been a brutal week. And I'm
OL,20,Fsort of getting through it."
