OL,3,CGordon Ramsay urges cyclists to wear
OL,4,Chelmets after 'really bad accident'
OL,6,FHe added that it was a "massive"
OL,7,Fweekend due to Father's Day, which
OL,8,Ftakes place on Sunday.
OL,10,FRamsay also captioned the post,
OL,11,Fwriting that he was "doing OK and did
OL,12,Fnot break any bones or suffer any
OL,13,Fmajor injuries, but I am a bit bruised
OL,14,Fup looking like a purple potato".
OL,16,FHe added that he was treated at
OL,17,FLawrence + Memorial Hospital in New
OL,18,FLondon, Connecticut, and the helmet
OL,19,F"saved" his life.
